text.title: Resilience 💪
text.paragraph: Born in the year of the Wood Ox, you possess an unwavering resilience that allows you to persevere through life's challenges. Your determination and strength are like an 🥃 oak tree, deeply rooted and unyielding.

text.title: Stability 🏡
text.paragraph: The Wood element brings a sense of stability and grounding to your personality. You value tradition and have a deep respect for family and cultural values. 🌳 Your solid foundation provides a sense of security and comfort.

text.title: Practicality 🔨
text.paragraph: With a practical and down-to-earth approach, you excel at tackling tasks methodically and efficiently. Your logical 🧠 mind and work ethic make you a reliable and dependable individual, capable of handling responsibilities with ease.

text.title: Loyalty 🤝
text.paragraph: Loyalty is one of your defining traits. Once you form a bond with someone, you remain steadfastly committed and dedicated, offering your unwavering 🛡️ support and protection to those you care about.

text.title: Patience 🕰️
text.paragraph: While you may sometimes come across as stubborn, your patience and ability to see the bigger picture are admirable qualities. 🐢 You understand that good things take time and are willing to wait for the right opportunities.
